    "description": "Help V-Hunter clear out a wide assortment of monsters in this dynamic turn-based grid puzzler! Tackle over 60 bite-sized levels in 5 different environments. Defeat 15 different enemy types using unique items such as Holy Water, Guns, and Dynamite to help you in your quest! <br><br><i>V-Hunter Puzzler Dx is a shorter experience. A single playthrough is estimated to take between 1-2 hours.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225430/extras/544c3a875025fd325d7679a52500af9d.poster.avif?t=1728014805\" width=764 height=428 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225430/extras/544c3a875025fd325d7679a52500af9d.webm?t=1728014805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225430/extras/544c3a875025fd325d7679a52500af9d.mp4?t=1728014805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamite! (and other items)</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Obliterate Mummies with Dynamite!<br></li><li>Use 5 other items, such as a Revolver to shoot from afar and Holy Water to damage Vampires!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225430/extras/6066fedb398c00dd096241ec2b61f29f.poster.avif?t=1728014805\" width=800 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225430/extras/6066fedb398c00dd096241ec2b61f29f.webm?t=1728014805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225430/extras/6066fedb398c00dd096241ec2b61f29f.mp4?t=1728014805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tons of Enemies</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>15 enemies with unique behavior<br></li><li>Slay Rats, Skeletons, Mummies, Demons, and more!<br></li><li>Boss fights too!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bite Sized Levels</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 60 levels<br></li><li>Each is designed to offer a challenge in just a few minutes</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225430/extras/d03f75eec1cf18a690433acab4076e7c.poster.avif?t=1728014805\" width=800 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225430/extras/d03f75eec1cf18a690433acab4076e7c.webm?t=1728014805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225430/extras/d03f75eec1cf18a690433acab4076e7c.mp4?t=1728014805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlockable Costumes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Complete achievements to unlock 6 unique costumes<br></li><li>Including Classic V, Jungle Fighter V, Reaper V, and more!</li></ul>",
